title: CDC, AIDS cases: number and rates of adults and adolescents, USA, 2004
name: CDC, AIDS cases: number and rates of adults and adolescents, USA, 2004
description:
This maps the number of AIDS cases reporte from 1998 to 2004 and the number of cases reported in 2004, as well as the 2004 rate (in cases per 100,000) and the prevalance at the end of 2004, mapped by select metropolitan statistical areas in the United States. 

Data obtained from CDC STD surveillance report 
Data URL: http://www.cdc.gov/hiv/topics/surveillance/resources/reports/2006supp_vol12no2/pdf/HIVAIDS_SSR_Vol12_No2.pdf
